{"tid":2247493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗︰推行國民教育是學校應有之責，青年融入國家發展刻不容緩，積極參與國內大循環。","createTime":"2020-10-18T01:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T06:02:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6a288870d09d294f84aeb547a335ddedb25265ec","tid":2247493,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:29:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/張建宗-青年認識國家刻不容緩-推國教是學校應有之責-010531292.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%98%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%88%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E7%B7%A9-%E6%8E%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%99%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E4%B9%8B%E8%B2%AC-010531292.html&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=878cc41c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/張建宗-青年認識國家刻不容緩-推國教是學校應有之責-010531292.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗指，幫助青年人認識國家和融入國家發展刻不容緩；而推行國民教育是學校應有之責。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗在網誌引述國家主席習近平，上周三在深圳經濟特區建立四十周年慶祝大會上發表的講話，認為對香港有非常重要的特殊意義。香港要加快與內地的融合，積極參與國內大循環。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又指，幫助青年人認識國家和融入國家發展刻不容緩；推行國民教育是學校應有之責，期望學校會做好國歌及國家安全教育工作，政府會支援學校及教師。"},{"pid":"5f877ea04bbdd8feb0c12648b038bd4d72b09634","tid":2247493,"uid":230530,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"張建宗啲狗仔狗女係外國定香港？"},{"pid":"c95b6254ab7cfd8233dd8fc0eff2733b6276b03f","tid":2247493,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdZgmTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdZgmTk.jpg&h=8cd65217&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2poXQMF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2poXQMF.png&h=d62d4d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOzTo6F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOzTo6F.jpg&h=a8af26e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src